Slingshot
===============================

There is a package for Slingshot in elementary Daily PPA:
$ sudo apt-add-repository ppa:elementary-os/daily
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install slingshot-launcher

This package is automatically updated everyday.

===============================

You can also compile Slingshot from source.
You need the following dependencies (on Ubuntu/Debian):
- cmake
- libgee-0.8-dev
- libgnome-menu-dev
- libgranite-dev (>= 0.3.0)
- libgtk-3-dev (>= 3.12)
- libjson-glib-dev
- libplank-dev (>= 0.9.0)
- libsoup2.4-dev
- libunity-dev
- libwnck-3-dev
- libzeitgeist-2.0-dev
- pkg-config
- valac (>= 0.26)
then:
$ mkdir build
$ cd build/
$ cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
$ make
$ sudo make install

===============================

